{"tid":2167293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日21/8 蘋果 有周庭畫像既全版廣告","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T06:34:56.000Z","uid":22556,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4624404beb93e041161708ce1aba1aa82d919ae5","tid":2167293,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeeS5uq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeeS5uq.jpg&h=4d5aef5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天刊登在蘋果日報的，Defiance &bull; Voices的全頁廣告。<br />\n<br />\n雖然事前已經知道和同意這個廣告的刊登，看到實物，還是有點震撼。<br />\n<br />\n自己的畫像能成為報紙的全頁廣告，當然是受寵若驚，也要感謝大家的厚愛。但同時大家不要忘記，在這片土地上，有很多很多人正在遭受比我更多的痛苦和壓力，他們或許寂寂無名，但卻為了這個家付出了未來。好好支援和支持他們，是我們的責任。<br />\n<br />\n#你今日買左蘋果未<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/622506141223354/posts/1765967693543854/?extid=0HuXPrYFZiyraHi5&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F622506141223354%2Fposts%2F1765967693543854%2F%3Fextid%3D0HuXPrYFZiyraHi5%26d%3Dn&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=3b8ffa92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/622506141223354/posts/1765967693543854/?extid=0HuXPrYFZiyraHi5&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/defiancevoices/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdefiancevoices%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=73cd5bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/defiancevoices/</a>"},{"pid":"d48b8fd05a00e57f2489332c36706c7c2025c1c2","tid":2167293,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"買咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddbf11ed77bf5b390222f801ec246b29355f236","tid":2167293,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.